        ## ç®€å•ä½¿ç”¨
        
        ### demo.py
        
        ```python
        import time
        from easy_clash_tool.clash import Clash
        
        clash = Clash(
            base_api='http://127.0.0.1:24621',
            secret='0367e21c-cceb-43a8-a2db-ad990e80dc28',
            group_name='',
        )
        
        # æ‰‹åŠ¨åˆ‡æ¢
        nodes, selected = clash.get_proxies()
        print(nodes)
        clash.change_node('ğŸ® Steam å•†åº—/ç¤¾åŒº')
        
        # è‡ªåŠ¨åˆ‡æ¢
        while True:
            clash.auto_switch()
            time.sleep(10)
        
        ```
        
